audio_sermons.title: Lift Up Your Eyes
audio_sermons.description: Don’t say that there is still plenty of time before the harvest. Jesus had a much different view. The regions are white already to harvest. Waiting around won’t make them more ripe. Lift up your eyes; there is something on the fringes of your vision. The numberless multitude of Heaven will be multi-cultural. Let’s keep stretching and lifting up our eyes!

audio_sermons.title: Married to Minister
audio_sermons.description: The purpose of marriage is to minister for God's glory. This message draws lessons from the life of Aquila and Priscilla, who gave themselves to selfless ministry. We have a responsibility to use our marriages to further God's Kingdom.
